com.jakub.premium.api

Interface User


  • public interface User
    The class represents a single user. The class has only getter methods. To change the user state, use the force methods from the App class. All getters methods (except for getUniqueId()) may return null values. All method names represent what they do, so they do not have any additional javadocs. ! It is not the final version of the API. It may be changed in next versions !
